com.wookler.zconfig.common.model

Class ConfigIncludeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode
      • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigElementNode
        • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigIncludeNode

  • public class ConfigIncludeNode
extends ConfigElementNode
    Configuration node that represents an external configuration set to be included under the current path.

    Included configurations are expected to be complete configuration sets.
